No matter the occasion, there’s a perfect drape waiting for you at VaraMahalakshmi Silks!

Whether you’re looking for traditional Muhurtham sarees, contemporary designs, or the latest trends, you’ll find it all under one roof at our 100 Ft Road showroom in Coimbatore.

With 15 showrooms across Tamil Nadu, VaraMahalakshmi Silks brings you an endless selection,  from rich Kanjeevarams and classic Banarasis to delicate Kota silks and elegant Organza sarees.

Every saree comes with our promise of 100% purity, ensuring you get the finest quality at the best price. There’s no need to compromise when it comes to tradition and elegance.

Our breathtaking Bridal Collection features intricate silver and gold zari weaves paired with rare and stunning colour combinations, making each silk saree truly one of a kind.

📍For a truly delightful shopping experience, visit us at @kanchivmlsilks, 100 Feet Road, Coimbatore.
